  <brief_title>Polaris - Crestor 40 mg vs Atorvastatin 80 mg for 26 Weeks</brief_title>
  <acronym>POLARIS</acronym>
  <official_title>A 26-Week, Double Blind, Randomised, Multi-Centre, Phase IIIb, Parallel Group Study to Compare the Efficacy and Safety of Rosuvastatin (40 mg) With Atorvastatin (80 mg) in Subjects With Hypercholesterolaemia and Coronary Heart Disease or CHD Risk Equivalents</official_title>
  <sponsors>
